| **Windows Event Viewer** | Built-in GUI utility to view and filter Windows logs |
| **Security Log** | Tracks authentication, account changes, policy modifications |
| **Application Log** | Tracks errors and events from running applications |
| **System Log** | Tracks driver issues, hardware events, startup/shutdown |

