## 🧩 MITRE ATT&CK Mapping

| Tactic | Technique | Description |
|---|---|---|
| **Persistence** | T1136.001 — Create Local Account | Attacker created a new user account to maintain access |
| **Privilege Escalation** | T1078 — Valid Accounts | Used the newly created/enabled account to operate |
| **Credential Access** | T1110 — Brute Force / Password Reset | Password reset observed on the target account |

