## 🔗 Cyber Kill Chain Phase

```
Reconnaissance → Weaponization → Delivery → Exploitation
       → Installation [HERE] → Command & Control → Actions on Objectives
```

The account creation and password reset map to the **Installation** phase — the attacker was establishing persistence before pivoting to the file server.

